article_title: Tennessee's Lamar Alexander off and running in new U.S. Senate

article_metadata.description: U.S. Sen. Lamar Alexander, R-Tenn., is among 22 Senate sponsors of the American Liberty Restoration Act, S. 203, a bill that repeals the requirement in the Affordable Care Act that requires people to have insurance.
